<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Feedback Survey</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/feedback-survey.css">
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="navbar-left">
                <a href="/" class="logo">Azania</a>
            </div>
            <div class="navbar-right">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/profile">Profile</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/visitor/dashboard">Visitor Dashboard</a></li>
                    <li>
                        <form action="/logout" method="POST" style="display:inline;">
                            <button type="submit" class="logout-btn">Logout</button>
                        </form>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="feedback-container">
            <h2>Feedback Survey</h2>
            <p>Please provide your feedback regarding your experience.</p>
    
            <form action="/visitor/submit-feedback" method="POST" class="form-grid">
            
                <!-- User Management -->
                <div>
                    <label>1. How easy was it to register or log in to the system?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Easy">Very Easy</option>
                        <option value="Easy">Easy</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Difficult">Difficult</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>2. Did you encounter any issues with account authentication or password recovery?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>If yes, please describe the issue:</label>
                    <textarea name="answers[]" rows="4"></textarea>
                </div>
            
                <!-- NLP Engine -->
                <div>
                    <label>3. Did the system correctly interpret your spoken or typed commands?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Always">Always</option>
                        <option value="Often">Often</option>
                        <option value="Sometimes">Sometimes</option>
                        <option value="Never">Never</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>4. How satisfied are you with the system's ability to process your input?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Satisfied">Very Satisfied</option>
                        <option value="Satisfied">Satisfied</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Unsatisfied">Unsatisfied</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Task Manager -->
                <div>
                    <label>5. Were your tasks (e.g., scheduling, routing calls) handled accurately by the system?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>6. How would you rate the overall effectiveness of task execution?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Effective">Very Effective</option>
                        <option value="Effective">Effective</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Ineffective">Ineffective</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>If there was an error, how well did the system handle task escalation?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Well">Very Well</option>
                        <option value="Well">Well</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Poorly">Poorly</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Security Integration -->
                <div>
                    <label>7. Did the system effectively manage access control for you or your visitors?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>8. Were the security checks for accessing restricted areas smooth?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Smooth">Very Smooth</option>
                        <option value="Smooth">Smooth</option>
                        <option value="Slightly Complicated">Slightly Complicated</option>
                        <option value="Complicated">Complicated</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Appointment Management -->
                <div>
                    <label>9. How easy was it to schedule an appointment using the system?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Easy">Very Easy</option>
                        <option value="Easy">Easy</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Difficult">Difficult</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>10. Did you receive timely confirmations and reminders for your appointments?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Call Routing -->
                <div>
                    <label>11. Was your call routed to the correct department or staff member?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Always">Always</option>
                        <option value="Most of the time">Most of the time</option>
                        <option value="Sometimes">Sometimes</option>
                        <option value="Never">Never</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>12. How effective was the call routing system?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Effective">Very Effective</option>
                        <option value="Effective">Effective</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Ineffective">Ineffective</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Query Management -->
                <div>
                    <label>13. Were your queries answered accurately and promptly?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>14. Did the system provide relevant data when you needed information?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>15. How would you rate your experience with the query management system?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Excellent">Excellent</option>
                        <option value="Good">Good</option>
                        <option value="Fair">Fair</option>
                        <option value="Poor">Poor</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Access Management -->
                <div>
                    <label>16. Did the system correctly identify your permissions for accessing restricted areas or functions?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>17. How easy was it to manage access permissions for visitors or staff?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Easy">Very Easy</option>
                        <option value="Easy">Easy</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Difficult">Difficult</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Visitor Logging -->
                <div>
                    <label>18. How seamless was the process of logging visitor information into the system?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Seamless">Very Seamless</option>
                        <option value="Seamless">Seamless</option>
                        <option value="Slightly Complicated">Slightly Complicated</option>
                        <option value="Complicated">Complicated</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>19. Were visitor records easy to retrieve when needed?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Peer Communication -->
                <div>
                    <label>20. Was the chat system helpful for communicating with staff members?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Helpful">Very Helpful</option>
                        <option value="Helpful">Helpful</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Not Helpful">Not Helpful</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>21. How frequently did you use the peer communication feature?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Frequently">Frequently</option>
                        <option value="Occasionally">Occasionally</option>
                        <option value="Rarely">Rarely</option>
                        <option value="Never">Never</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Data Fetching -->
                <div>
                    <label>22. Were you able to fetch relevant data (e.g., appointments, records) when needed?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>23. How would you rate the system's ability to fetch accurate data?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Excellent">Excellent</option>
                        <option value="Good">Good</option>
                        <option value="Fair">Fair</option>
                        <option value="Poor">Poor</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Escalation System -->
                <div>
                    <label>24. Did the system escalate tasks when it could not resolve your request?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>25. How satisfied were you with the escalation and resolution process?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Satisfied">Very Satisfied</option>
                        <option value="Satisfied">Satisfied</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Unsatisfied">Unsatisfied</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Notification System -->
                <div>
                    <label>26. Were notifications (email/SMS/in-app) sent promptly for your tasks and appointments?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Always">Always</option>
                        <option value="Most of the time">Most of the time</option>
                        <option value="Sometimes">Sometimes</option>
                        <option value="Never">Never</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>27. Did you find the notifications helpful in managing your tasks?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Helpful">Very Helpful</option>
                        <option value="Helpful">Helpful</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Not Helpful">Not Helpful</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Visitor Pass Issuance -->
                <div>
                    <label>28. How easy was it to request a visitor pass through the system?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Easy">Very Easy</option>
                        <option value="Easy">Easy</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Difficult">Difficult</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>29. Was the pass issuance process smooth and timely?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Smooth">Very Smooth</option>
                        <option value="Smooth">Smooth</option>
                        <option value="Slightly Complicated">Slightly Complicated</option>
                        <option value="Complicated">Complicated</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Feedback System -->
                <div>
                    <label>30. How likely are you to provide feedback after using the system or completing tasks?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Likely">Very Likely</option>
                        <option value="Likely">Likely</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Unlikely">Unlikely</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>31. How satisfied are you with the feedback options and ease of submission?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Satisfied">Very Satisfied</option>
                        <option value="Satisfied">Satisfied</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Unsatisfied">Unsatisfied</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <!-- Feedback Reporting -->
                <div>
                    <label>32. How well does the system compile and present feedback data for review?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Very Well">Very Well</option>
                        <option value="Well">Well</option>
                        <option value="Neutral">Neutral</option>
                        <option value="Poorly">Poorly</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div>
                    <label>33. Do you feel that your feedback leads to improvements or changes in the system?</label>
                    <select name="answers[]" required>
                        <option value="Yes">Yes</option>
                        <option value="No">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            
                <div class="full-width">
                    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <span>&copy; Azania. All Rights Reserved.</span>
        <span>Privacy</span>
        <span>Terms</span>
        <span>FAQs</span>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
